divs: Sighting Detailsi just remember seeing it in the sky it was quiet and still ,it had squarelike panels changing colors rapidly,red,yellow,blue? it was around my birthday,me and some freinds were camping in my backyard. i just remember looking at itfor maybe 10-15 min.i do not recall it leaving. even being 12 yrs. old i almost new it was something abnormal.i dont remember much more at this time.
